'''Nadege Uwamwezi''' (wavutse 1993), ni umukinnyi wa filimi mu  [[Rwanda]] <ref>https://umuryango.rw/imyidagaduro/article/nadege-uwamwezi-wamenyekanye-nka-nana-muri-filime-city-maid-aragaragaza</ref>. Umwe mu bakinnyi ba filime bazwi cyane muri filimi zo kuri televiziyo  mu [[Rwanda]], Nadege azwi cyane ku ruhare 'Nana' mu biganiro bya televiziyo, ''City Maid'' <ref>https://umuryango.rw/imyidagaduro/article/nadege-uwamwezi-wamenyekanye-nka-nana-muri-filime-city-maid-aragaragaza</ref>.  Usibye gukina, ni n'umuririmbyi n'munyamideri.<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/topics/nadege-uwamwezi</ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse mu 1993 mu Rwanda. Yafunguye butike yitwa 'Nana Fashion Shop' ifite izina rye.  Afite umuhungu umwe kuva yashyingiranwa bwa mbere, Ganza Benny Lucky<ref>http://rwanda.shafaqna.com/EN/AL/172611</ref>. Nkâ€™uko ibihuha bivugwa, ngo yaba akundana n'umuririmbyi [[Kizito Mihigo]]<ref>https://rwandapaparazzi.rw/2019/09/13/nana-wo-muri-city-maid-yavuze-ku-byurukundo-rwe-na-kizito-mihigoinkuru/</ref> . Ariko nyuma yaje kubihakana, avuga ko ari inshuti gusa. Icyakora, vuba aha byavuzwe ko bategura ubukwe. Icyakora, yongeye guhakana ibyo aregwa<ref>https://frankensaurus.com/Nadege_Uwamwezi</ref>.

== Umwuga ==
Mbere yo gukina, Nadege yari umuririmbyi waririmbye ku izina rya 'Umwamikazi Nadege'. Yari mu itsinda ryitwa 'The Queens' aho baririmbaga 'Ryajambo' mu 2009. <ref>https://inyarwanda.com/inkuru/63638/nadege-uwamwezi--63638.html</ref>Yinjiye muri Kwetu Film Institute yiga ikinamico. Nyuma, yamenyekanye gukina na Kennedy Mazimpaka, amaze kubona ubuhanga bwe bwo gukina i Kwetu<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/entertainment/acting-can-earn-you-decent-life-says-actress-uwamwezi</ref>. Mazimpaka yamuhaye uruhare ruto muri filime ''Rwasibo'', yaje kuba umukinnyi wa mbere wa sinema.  Mu mwaka wa 2016, yakinnye muri filimi ica kuri televiziyo ''Mutoni'' nk'uruhare rwo kuyobora.<ref>https://eng.inyarwanda.com/index.php/inkuru/68227/seburikoko-collected-4-trophies-at-rwanda-movie-awards-2016-68227.html</ref> 

Nyuma, yakinnye muri firime nyinshi zizwi cyane na  zirimo, ''Catherine'' na ''Nkubito ya Nyamunsi'' . Muri 2016, yakinnye muri ''City Maid''<ref>https://inyarwanda.com/inkuru/102018/nana-wamamaye-muri-city-maid-yahishuye-ko-hari-abamusaba-kuryamana-na-we-batazi-ko-ari-umu-102018.html</ref> . filimi imaze kumenyekana cyane mubantu kandi yakundaga kwitwa 'Nana'.<ref>https://igihe.com/imyidagaduro/article/umukinnyi-wa-filime-nana-agiye-gukora-ubukwe-n-umusore-uba-mu-bubiligi</ref> 

